PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of ROSLYN KUNIN, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Doreen Braverman, whose term has expired.
